cipient of a benefit, annuity, or refund shall be recovered, as applicable, from the member, participant, former member, former participant, or beneficiary. This paragraph excludes amounts overpaid pursuant to paragraph (2), (3), or (4).</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(2) All amounts that have been overpaid due to inaccurate information, untimely submission, or nonsubmission of information by an employer
