d the plan is regulated by the federal Employee Retirement Income Security Act of 1974 (29 U.S.C. Sec. 1001 et seq.).</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(b) The benefit plan required by this article shall apply to public employees who are new members as defined in Section 7522.04.</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(c) (1) Individuals who were employed by any public employer before January 1, 2013, and who became employed by a subsequent public employer for the first time on or after January 1, 2013, shall be subject to the retirement plan that would have been
